{"tid":2366592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東莞51歲女子染疫 為香港跨境貨車司機密切接觸者","createTime":"2021-01-14T15:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T04:35:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a2a7c7d5aae2d98ede075ffbf17436df7c72ca","tid":2366592,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:24:28.000Z","msg":"回港易 拍拍拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛剛通報：#東莞新增1例無症狀感染者#！1月14日，我市新增1例無症狀感染者，系1月12日深圳通報香港籍跨境貨車司機林某某的密切接觸者。情況如下：<br />\n<br />\n莫某某，女，51歲，橋頭鎮石水口村開業紙品廠會計，家住橋頭鎮凱逸豪庭小區。<br />\n<br />\n1月11日，港籍司機林某某初篩結果呈陽性後，莫某某被判定為林某某的密切接觸者，當晚接受集中隔離醫學觀察，當天新冠病毒核酸檢測結果為陰性。<br />\n<br />\n1月13日，莫某某再次接受採樣檢測。1月14日凌晨，市疾控中心檢測結果呈陽性，隨即被轉運至市定點救治醫院市第九人民醫院隔離治療，目前情況穩定。"},{"pid":"840d5fd753fdf2e262c651da020161c005e2140d","tid":2366592,"uid":88743,"like":22,"dislike":5,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"人地揸車送貨去東莞啫<br />\n又關叫雞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c74327c3373909895a354287086dcc786283d0c","tid":2366592,"uid":2054,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"濃厚接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f0aca995ec638470e498d40f69181d9a56dc34","tid":2366592,"uid":378793,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"邊位連登仔老豆呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55834cda108fa3378459ea41c3cf0c9c49346b1b","tid":2366592,"uid":165136,"like":4,"dislike":32,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T